---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../../../styles/busan.css';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Day 2 · 海雲台藍線 · 天空膠囊夕陽場"
  description="釜山 7 日 Day 2：海里丹路咖啡、X The Sky 100 樓、天空膠囊夕陽場、廣安木乾式熟成烤肉。"
>
  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href={base}>首頁</a>
        <span class="breadcrumb-separator">/</span>
        <a href={`${base}/travel`}>旅遊</a>
        <span class="breadcrumb-separator">/</span>
        <a href={`${base}/travel/busan`}>釜山</a>
        <span class="breadcrumb-separator">/</span>
        <span>Day 2</span>
      </nav>

      <header class="busan-hero d2">
        <div class="busan-hero-inner">
          <span class="day-badge">DAY 2 · 6 / 17（二）</span>
          <h1>海雲台藍線 · <span class="accent">天空膠囊夕陽場</span></h1>
          <p class="subtitle">海里丹路咖啡 → X The Sky 100 樓 → 尾浦到青沙浦的<strong>夕陽膠囊列車</strong>，最後乾式熟成烤肉收尾。今天的主軸是「海邊的一切」。</p>
          <div class="meta-pills">
            <span>☕ 海里丹路咖啡</span>
            <span>🏙 100 樓全市景</span>
            <span>🚞 17:00 夕陽膠囊</span>
            <span>🥩 廣安木熟成肉</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class="busan-section">
        <h2>📋 今日行程</h2>
        <ol class="timeline">
          <li class="timeline-item food">
            <div class="num">1</div>
            <div class="item-card">
              <div class="time">10:30</div>
              <div class="title">海里丹路 해리단길 早午餐 + 咖啡</div>
              <p class="desc">海雲台站旁的文青小巷弄。<strong>DUPLIT</strong> 是熱門選擇，也可以挑一間順眼的店進去。</p>
              <div class="tags"><span class="tag">美食</span><span class="tag">咖啡</span><span class="tag">早午餐</span></div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="timeline-item">
            <div class="num">2</div>
            <div class="item-card">
              <div class="time">13:00</div>
              <div class="title">Busan X The Sky 100 樓展望台</div>
              <p class="desc">LCT 大樓 100 樓，世界最高星巴克就在這。可以一次把海雲台、廣安大橋、五六島盡收眼底。</p>
              <div class="tags"><span class="tag">景點</span><span class="tag">展望</span><span class="tag">通行證可選</span></div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="timeline-item must">
            <div class="num">3</div>
            <div class="item-card">
              <div class="time">17:00</div>
              <div class="title">天空膠囊列車（尾浦 → 青沙浦）<span class="star">⭐</span></div>
              <p class="desc">夕陽場最美，務必<strong>提前 1–2 週</strong>訂！列車慢慢沿海岸滑行，整路都是海。</p>
              <div class="tags"><span class="tag">必訂</span><span class="tag">夕陽</span><span class="tag warn">不在通行證內</span></div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="timeline-item">
            <div class="num">4</div>
            <div class="item-card">
              <div class="time">18:30</div>
              <div class="title">青沙浦 · 灌籃高手平交道 + 海岸散步</div>
              <p class="desc">青沙浦是個漁村，以紅白雙塔燈塔聞名。回程改搭<strong>海岸列車</strong>（Visit Busan Pass 可免費），慢慢看海回到尾浦。</p>
              <div class="tags"><span class="tag">景點</span><span class="tag">拍照</span></div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="timeline-item food">
            <div class="num">5</div>
            <div class="item-card">
              <div class="time">19:30</div>
              <div class="title">廣安木 海雲台店（晚餐）</div>
              <p class="desc">乾式熟成烤肉名店。記得提前訂位，建議用 Naver Map 內建訂位或請飯店幫忙。</p>
              <div class="tags"><span class="tag">美食</span><span class="tag">烤肉</span><span class="tag warn">需訂位</span></div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section class="busan-section">
        <h2>💡 今日小提醒</h2>
        <div class="warn-box">
          <h4>⚠️ 天空膠囊列車不在 Visit Busan Pass 內</h4>
          <p>很多人以為可以用通行證進，但<strong>它不在 Big 5 名單</strong>，要單獨在 Klook / KKday 訂，夕陽場很搶手，至少提前 1–2 週。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tip-box">
          <h4>單買海岸列車 ₩7,000 比較划算</h4>
          <p>海岸列車（不是膠囊列車）票價便宜，Big 5 名額留給更貴的景點（樂天、Luge、Club D Oasis）。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tip-box">
          <h4>Thrill On The Mug 為什麼今天不去？</h4>
          <p>這家影島超紅的海景咖啡<strong>每週二公休</strong>，所以排到 <a href={`${base}/travel/busan/day7`}>Day 7（週日）</a>。</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <nav class="day-nav">
        <a href={`${base}/travel/busan/day1`}>
          <div class="label">← DAY 1</div>
          <div class="ttl">抵達 → 海雲台</div>
        </a>
        <a href={`${base}/travel/busan/day3`} class="next">
          <div class="label">DAY 3 →</div>
          <div class="ttl">東釜山 · 龍宮寺 + 樂天 + 帝王蟹</div>
        </a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
